The rating on this game is far lower than it deserves. I hear it had some bugs at 1st. The game runs smoothly now. The art is unique and vibrant. The combat of the character is simple. If you die then your character dies and you start 100 years later as a new Sword Of Ditto. You gradually improve through eras of hero.
